rtment_syllabus?lectureNo=1793&departmentNo=119\">感染症リスク解析</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1794&departmentNo=119\">ブロックチェーン経済入門 </a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1795&departmentNo=119\">知恵することー情報の視点から生命と社会の本質を考える</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1816&departmentNo=119\">知恵することー情報の視点から生命と社会の本質を考える</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1796&departmentNo=119\">サービスラーニングA・B</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1797&departmentNo=119\">ビジネスアナリティクス応用</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1798&departmentNo=119\">人新世の人文学</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1799&departmentNo=119\">マインドフルネス：東洋と西洋の間</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1825&departmentNo=119\">マインドフルネス：東洋と西洋の間</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1800&departmentNo=119\">人文科学的空間論I</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                <div class=\"syllabusTitle\">\r\n                    <a href=\"department_syllabus?lectureNo=1801&departmentNo=119\">人文科学的空間論II</a>\r\n                        </div>\r\n  